    <h1>Add Additional Dependant</h1>
    <br />
    <p class="radialShadow">&nbsp;</p>
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:939px">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p>
                    Who can be registered as a dependant?
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your spouse or partner </li>
                    <li>Dependant children under the age of 21 </li>
                    <li>Dependant children over the age of 21 but under the age of 25 and is a full time
                        student at a recognised tertiary educational institution. </li>
                    <li>Immediate family for which the member is liable for family care and support. (Proof
                        of legal duty required.) </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Existing CompCare Wellness members can add a dependant by completing the necessary application
                    form.  Please select the form from the table below:
                </p>
                <table cellspacing="0" align="center">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="on">
                                Type
                            </th>
                            <th style="width:300px">
                                Link
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="priceBody">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="on">
                                <img src="../Images/pdfIcon.png" alt="" />
                            </td>
                            <td style="width:300px">
                                <a href="../Downloads/MembershipApplicationForm.pdf" target="_blank">&raquo;
                                    Add Additional Dependant Form</a>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="on">
                            </td>
                            <td style="width:300px">
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
                <p>
                    Please attach the following documents to the application form if applicable to the
                    dependant:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Previous medical scheme membership certificates </li>
                    <li>Copy of ID’s for adults and birth certificates for children </li>
                    <li>Marriage certificate </li>
                    <li>An affidavit should surnames differ or a common law spouse or partner are added
                        as dependant </li>
                    <li>Adopted children –legal documentation to be provided.</li>
                    <li>Student certificate and / or
                        proof of registration from the university or college if a child dependant is studying.</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
